  <description>
    <p>Froststrap is a cross-platform bootstrapper/launcher for Roblox, written in C#. It is a fork of Fishstrap (which itself is a fork of Bloxstrap), focused on performance, customization, and additional features.</p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customizable bootstrapper launcher with themes and backgrounds</li>
      <li>Multi-mod system with hex code generation</li>
      <li>FastFlag management with profiles</li>
      <li>Discord Rich Presence integration</li>
      <li>Multi-instance launching support</li>
      <li>Account manager</li>
      <li>Game shortcuts and region selector</li>
      <li>Automatic rejoin on inactivity disconnect</li>
      <li>Playtime counter (total and session)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
